Alejandro Rey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alejandro_Rey 0 Alejandro Rey (February 8, 1930 – May 21, 1987) was an Argentine-American actor and television director. He emigrated to the United States in 1960, later became a United States citizen, and gained his widest acclaim there. He had a son, Brandon, with his former wife Joyce Rey.
